Release Notes
Fabio Valentini Pro Scalper [PickMyTrade]

Inspired by Fabio Valentini’s NASDAQ scalping methodology, this strategy approximates institutional order flow concepts using volume-based analysis for liquid markets.

Core Concepts:
Volume Profile (POC, VAH, VAL) to identify institutional price acceptance zones.
Delta approximation to estimate buying vs selling pressure using candle volume distribution.
Absorption detection using high-volume, low-range candles to identify passive institutional activity.
Triple-A model based on absorption, accumulation, and aggression phases.

Entry Types:
Triple-A breakout setups with volume confirmation.
Opening Range Breakouts (configurable, default 30 minutes).
Value Area High / Value Area Low reactions with absorption confirmation.

Key Features:
VWAP with ATR-based dynamic bands.
Session-based filtering (default NY session).
Built-in risk management, daily loss limit, and optional ATR trailing stops.
Real-time dashboard and configurable signal filters.

Important Notes:
This script does not use true order flow. It approximates institutional behavior using TradingView volume data and is intended for educational purposes only. Strategy performance is highly sensitive to commissions, slippage, parameter selection, and market conditions.

Disclaimer:
This is not financial advice. Past performance does not guarantee future results. Users are responsible for their own testing, risk management, and execution quality.
